
Test case 1: Positive LogIn test
Open page
Type username practice into Username field
Type password SuperSecretPassword! into Password field
Push Submit button
Verify new page URL contains practice.expandtesting.com/secure
Verify new page contains expected text ('Welcome to the Secure Area' or 'You logged into a secure area!')
Verify link Logout is displayed on the new page

Test case 2: Negative username test
Open page
Type username incorrectUser into Username field
Type password SuperSecretPassword! into Password field
Push Submit button
Verify error message is displayed
Verify error message text is Your username is invalid!

Test case 3: Negative password test
Open page
Type username student into Username field
Type password incorrectPassword into Password field
Push Submit button
Verify error message is displayed
Verify error message text is Your password is invalid!



